oducing kernel of the Fock space and as\nintegral kernel of the Segal-Bargmann transform. As a corollary to our\nconstruction we also obtain the integral kernel of the unitary inversion\noperator in the Schr\\\"odinger model in terms of a multivariable $J$-Bessel\nfunction as well as explicit Whittaker vectors.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 23 May 2012 13:58:12 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 12 Jun 2012 09:09:11 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 23 Nov 2012 08:01:57 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Wed, 19 Jun 2013 11:58:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-03-19"}
